lead_paragraph: India spinners Ravichandran Ashwin and Jayant Yadav claimed three wickets apiece in the second innings to lead the hosts to a comfortable 246-run win in the second test against England on Monday and a 1-0 lead in the five-match series.

headline.print_headline: Spinners Wrap Up India Win Over England in Second Test
